      <header>
                    <h2 class="node__title node-title"><a href="content/where-it-all-going-prospects-human-future">Where Is It All Going? Prospects for the Human Future</a></h2>
            <span property="dc:title" content="Where Is It All Going? Prospects for the Human Future" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>
              <p class="submitted">
                    <span property="dc:date dc:created" content="2016-10-05T23:02:23-04:00" datatype="xsd:dateTime" rel="sioc:has_creator">Submitted by <span class="username" xml:lang="" about="/users/lisa" typeof="sioc:UserAccount" property="foaf:name" datatype="">Lisa</span> on <time pubdate datetime="2016-10-05T23:02:23-04:00">Wed, 2016-10-05 23:02</time></span>        </p>
      
          </header>
  
    
    <div class="field field-name-field-summary field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p><strong>Abstract: </strong>Society now faces many major, even existential, issues that threaten our future. At the same time that accelerating changes are converging to create enormous potential problems, prospective synergistic solution spaces are emerging that offer strategies—and hope—for the human future. <strong>By Dennis M. Bushnell</strong></p>
</div></div></div>
  <ul class="links inline"><li class="node-readmore first last"><a href="content/where-it-all-going-prospects-human-future" rel="tag" title="Where Is It All Going? Prospects for the Human Future">Read more<span class="element-invisible"> about Where Is It All Going? Prospects for the Human Future</span></a></li>
</ul>
  
